    <x:String x:Key="TxtSettingsTitle">Settings</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSettingsDesc">Manage application preferences</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtAppPrefs">App Preferences</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtCacheMgmt">Local cache &amp; Default version management</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtCacheDesc">View and manage downloaded component versions, set default versions for Quick Install and game management, and free up local storage space.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtManage">&#xE8B7;  Manage</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtLanguage">Application Language</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtLanguageDesc">Change the user interface language.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtClose">Close</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGotIt">Got it</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtAppRepoTitle">App Repository</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtAppRepoDesc">Target GitHub repository for updates and feedback (Owner/RepoName).</x:String>
    <!-- Guide Window -->
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideTitle">Guide</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideHeader">How to use Optiscaler Client</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideHeaderDesc">Simple steps to enhance your games</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep1Title">1. Find your games</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep1Desc">Click the 'Scan Games' button to let the app automatically find installed games from Steam, Epic, GOG, or Xbox. Check the 'Add Manually' button if you have a standalone game.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep2Title">2. Manage a game</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep2Desc">Next to your game in the list, click 'Manage'. A window will open allowing you to install or update the OptiScaler mod for that specific game.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep3Title">3. Install OptiScaler</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep3Desc">Inside the Management window, choose your OptiScaler version and options. Use 'Auto Install' for a quick setup. If Auto Install fails or cannot find the correct executable (.exe), use 'Manual Install' to select the game's executable yourself.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep4Title">4. Play the game</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtGuideStep4Desc">Once installed, start your game normally. Inside the game, bring up the OptiScaler menu using the 'Insert' key to tweak your settings!</x:String>

