    <x:String x:Key="TxtTooltipOptiScalerVersion">Select the specific version of OptiScaler you want to install for this game.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtTooltipInjectionMethod">Determines how OptiScaler is loaded. Common choices are dxgi.dll or version.dll depending on the game compatibility.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtTooltipFsr4Int8">Injects the FSR 4 INT8 mod DLL. This allows non-RDNA 4 GPUs to use FSR 4 features. Select 'None' if you have an RX 9000 series (RDNA 4) GPU.</x:String>

