    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterOptions">Filter Options</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterShowAllTitle">Scan all games</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterShowAllDesc">Detect and show all installed games from all enabled sources.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterHideTitle">Scan all, hide games without upscalers</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterHideDesc">Scan everything, but automatically hide games with no detectable DLSS, FSR, or XeSS. Hidden games remain in the list and can be shown from Organize mode.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterSkipTitle">Skip games without upscalers</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterSkipDesc">Only include games where DLSS, FSR, or XeSS DLLs are detected.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFilterSkipWarning">Some games support upscalers but do not expose their DLLs in a detectable path. Those games will not appear in the list.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtShowNonGameApps">Show games without upscalers (DLSS/FSR/XeSS)</x:String>
